        public Velocity(int deltaX,
        int deltaY,
        long deltaTime,
        long velocitySampleTime,
        int xPlacement,
        int yPlacement,
        float sampleDensity)
        Creates a new velocity object from the change in x, y and time
        Parameters:
        deltaX - Change in x between two sample points
        deltaY - Change in y between two sample points
        deltaTime - Time between the two samplePoints
        sampleTime - The time at which the second sample was taken
        xPlacment - The x coordinate of the starting point of the velocity vecotr
        yPlacemnt - The y coordinate of the starting point of the velocity vector
        sampleDensity - Density of the system at the time of the sample
